" title=\"\"><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our next destination was the capital city, <strong>Delhi<\/strong>. With a well-planned itinerary, we comfortably explored the city without rushing.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Places we visited:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>India Gate<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Qutub Minar<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Humayun\u2019s Tomb<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Lotus Temple<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Raj Ghat<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Red Fort (drive past)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The mix of Mughal architecture, modern streets, and vibrant markets made Delhi a memorable part of our journey.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Jaipur \u2013 The Royal Pink City Experience<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/assets.architecturaldigest.in\/photos\/65eac7d319a94828e60c5799\/master\/w_1600%2Cc_limit\/_DSC3575%2520%281%29.jpg\" alt=\"Ornate royal corridor inside Jaipur City Palace featuring carved pillars, traditional Rajasthani wall art, chandeliers, and polished red flooring\" title=\"\"><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1918\" src=\"https:\/\/manuadventuresindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Hawa_Mahal_at_Sunrise2C_Jaipur_-_panoramio-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Hawa Mahal Jaipur sunrise view showcasing the iconic pink sandstone facade and intricate lattice windows\" class=\"wp-image-18806\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/manuadventuresindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Hawa_Mahal_at_Sunrise2C_Jaipur_-_panoramio-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/manuadventuresindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Hawa_Mahal_at_Sunrise2C_Jaipur_-_panoramio-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/manuadventuresindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Hawa_Mahal_at_Sunrise2C_Jaipur_-_panoramio-1024x767.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/manuadventuresindia.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/Hawa_Mahal_at_Sunrise2C_Jaipur_-_panoramio-768x575.jpg 768w, https:\/\/manuadventuresindia.com\/w